

used to + simple verb(main form)



I used to smoke.

You used to watch TV a lot befor comming to this class.

It used to be foggy in the morning.

We used to live in Yazd but now we live in tehran.

They used to work here but for some reasons the boss fired them from the company.

You didn't used to work out , what happend to you?

He didn't used to drive so fast befor visiting her!

We didn't used to travel a lot because our city's weather was usually rainy.

Did you used to run every morning in the school?

Did she used to make her bed? ==>   cleaning bed

Where did you used to shop?

How much food did he used to eat?
